title: InitializeEmptyPropertyInstance (Function)
text:
FUNCTION InitializeEmptyPropertyInstance : BOOL
Initializes a property (prop) with its (working) defaults (mostly empty) considering constant array sizes, lists and special property types.

rows.Name: objTyp
rows.Comment: The object instance which has the desired property.

rows:
The access specifier used for initializing the property
instance.

The property ID of the property for which the instance data
shall be initialized.
